cards.title: Infinite Runner
cards.information: Infinite Runner is an exhilarating and visually stunning infinite runner game developed in C# using the Unity game engine. In this game, players embark on an epic journey through a narrow landscape, dodging obstacles, collecting power-ups, and aiming for the highest score.
